name: FClothConstraintSetupNv
doc: Container for a constraint setup, these can be horizontal, vertical, shear and bend.

Stiffness: How stiff this constraint is, this affects how closely it will follow the desired position
StiffnessMultiplier: A multiplier affecting the above value
StretchLimit: The hard limit on how far this constraint can stretch
CompressionLimit: The hard limit on how far this constraint can compress
